OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1782047474
OL,3,CTartan Army fans still keeping World
OL,4,CCup dream alive despite Morocco defeat
OL,6,FThe Tartan Army ranks that have
OL,7,Finvaded Boston remained confident
OL,8,Ftheir World Cup journey can still
OL,9,Fextend beyond the group stages despite
OL,10,Fthe disappointment of defeat to
OL,11,FMorocco.
OL,13,FMorocco's winning goal, coming only 71
OL,14,Fseconds into Friday's match, quickly
OL,15,Fburst the exuberant mood that had
OL,16,Fbuilt among Scotland fans in
OL,17,FMassachusetts throughout the day.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
