FL,320,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1782047474
OL,3,CTartan Army fans still keeping World
OL,4,CCup dream alive despite Morocco defeat
OL,6,FDespondency turned to frustration and
OL,7,Fanger among the travelling contingent
OL,8,Famid a feeling that the team were
OL,9,Fdenied at least one, potentially two,
OL,10,Fsecond-half penalties.
OL,12,FBut by full-time there was a sense of
OL,13,Fdefiance with many supporters already
OL,14,Fturning their thoughts to the final
OL,15,Fgroup game against Brazil in Miami on
OL,16,FWednesday and insisting the point that
OL,17,Fwould all but guarantee history-making
OL,18,Fprogress from the group could be
OL,19,Fsecured against the five-time world
OL,20,Fchampions.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
