OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,320,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1782047474
OL,3,CTartan Army fans still keeping World
OL,4,CCup dream alive despite Morocco defeat
OL,6,F"We've really got to win against
OL,7,FBrazil. I said Morocco is one of the
OL,8,Fbest teams in the world and Brazil is
OL,9,Fslacking a little bit, so we've got a
OL,10,Fchance."
OL,12,FAberdonian Stuart Insh, who is 45 and
OL,13,Flives in Edinburgh, said he felt a
OL,14,Fsense of "deflation".
OL,16,F"Hopefully, the town of Boston is
OL,17,Fstill happy with our company that
OL,18,Fwe're now sort of not as quite in the
OL,19,Fsame bravado as we were before the
OL,20,Fgame," he said.
