OL,3,CTartan Army fans still keeping World
OL,4,CCup dream alive despite Morocco defeat
OL,6,FOrange traffic cones have been spotted
OL,7,Fon statues all over the city since the
OL,8,FTartan Army came to town.
OL,10,FPre match on Friday, there were also a
OL,11,Ffew on fans' heads too amid as they
OL,12,Fagain showed the World Cup why it is
OL,13,F"No Scotland, No Party".
OL,15,FThe cone tradition, which has become a
OL,16,Fcalling card for travelling Scotland
OL,17,Ffans, is most associated with the
OL,18,Fstatue of the Duke of Wellington
OL,19,Foutside the Gallery of Modern Art in
OL,20,FGlasgow.
OL,26,@uD@AOUuD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
