PN,31911
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1782047474
OL,3,CTartan Army fans still keeping World
OL,4,CCup dream alive despite Morocco defeat
OL,6,FSince the late 1980s, a cone has been
OL,7,Fon the statue's head and has been
OL,8,Fpersistently replaced whenever it is
OL,9,Fremoved.
OL,11,FEven Boston mayor Michelle Wu has got
OL,12,Fin on the act, admitting to placing a
OL,13,Fcone on the head of a statue of Boston
OL,14,FCeltics basketball great Bill Russell
OL,15,Fduring a week when Bostonians have
OL,16,Ftaken Scotland fans to their heart.
OL,18,FCaroline Warren from Connecticut
OL,19,Fjoined Scotland supporters watching
OL,20,FFriday night's game in a bar in
OL,21,Fcentral Boston.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
