CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1782047474
OL,3,CTartan Army fans still keeping World
OL,4,CCup dream alive despite Morocco defeat
OL,6,F"No matter what, you guys have the
OL,7,Fbest fans ever," she said.
OL,9,F"Like, genuinely, you guys have won
OL,10,Fthe World Cup of fans."
